Reasoning: The paper discusses efficient minimum mean square error (MMSE) frequency domain equalization (FDE)-based iterative (turbo) packet combining for broadband MIMO CDMA systems with Chase-type ARQ. This involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), communication (cs.COMM), systems and control (cs.SY), and multimedia (cs.MM).
